                <span>1. </span>
                <span style=3D"margin-left: 10px;word-break: break-word;">N=
ame                             Date<br>LIQUID VOLUME CONVERSION CHART<br>U=
S CUSTOMARY UNITS (PRECISE)<br>Please note that these conversions work for =
US customary units only.<br>                  STANDARD -&gt; METRIC CONVERS=
IONS<br> 1 tablespoon =3D             3 teaspoons         =3D 14.78677 mill=
